content: So this does 1 part of the process, I think if it does it well enough, we should just use it. If we can stitch together things and make it so all AI needs is data like you have on me to fully automate the process, and it's just stitching together a bunch of different solutions, then that would still be unique right? Like maybe its the pre-outreach and scheduling responses or negotiations, whatever, it just does it?
